| Param                 | Purpose                   | Example                           |
| --------------------- | ------------------------- | --------------------------------- |
| `title`               | Search job title          | `Data Engineer`                   |
| `location`            | Filter by location        | `United States OR United Kingdom` |
| `time_frame`          | Freshness window          | `24h`, `7d`, `6m`                 |
| `limit`               | Results per request       | `100`                             |
| `offset`              | Pagination                | `0`, `100`, `200`                 |
| `description_format`  | Include description       | `text`                            |
| `organization`        | Specific company          | `Google`                          |
| `organization_slug`   | Exact company slug        | `google`                          |
| `seniority`           | Experience level          | `Entry level`, `Mid-Senior level` |
| `ai_experience_level` | Years of experience       | `0-2`, `2-5`, `5-10`              |
| `ai_work_arrangement` | Remote/Hybrid/Onsite      | `Remote Solely`                   |
| `ai_employment_type`  | Full-time, Contract, etc. | `FULL_TIME`                       |
| `has_salary`          | Only jobs with salary     | `true`                            |
| `organization_agency` | Exclude recruiters        | `exclude`                         |
| `direct_apply`        | Easy Apply jobs           | `only`                            |
| Param                   | Example                         |
| ----------------------- | ------------------------------- |
| `title_advanced`        | `(data & engineer) & !senior`   |
| `description_advanced`  | `python & (aws \| azure)`       |
| `location_advanced`     | `'United States' & !California` |
| `organization_advanced` | `(Google \| Microsoft)`         |
